Memberships
Be One of Us!
Whether you have been golfing your entire life, or have just begun to appreciate the game, Golf Central Golf Club offers a membership option that suits you. Our challenging course and friendly staff ensures our members will enjoy bringing guests out for a drink, as well as perfecting their game.
We encourage you to request a tour of our facility, and welcome any questions you may have. For additional information about pricing and our application process, please fill out this form or call us at 352.489.4566. We look forward to hearing from you.
Inquire Now
Membership Options
Memberships
Rates
Single all inclusive
$2,700 +tax
Family all inclusive
$3,600 + tax
Includes green fees & cart fees, range balls, GHIN handicap service, 10% off merchandise
Memberships
Rates
Executive Single
$2,000 +tax
Executive Family
$2,800 +tax
Includes green fees & cart fees after 12:45 Monday-Friday and all day on weekends and holidays, range balls, GHIN handicap service, 10% off merchandise.
Inquire Now
Introducing the 2025 Player’s Pass!
As a 2025 Player’s Pass Member, you’ll get
Enjoy a full year of golf savings with access to reduced rates, no restrictions, and carts included! Plus, get 10% off Pro Shop merchandise and equipment. As a 2025 Player’s Pass Member, you’ll also benefit from a 2-week booking window and easy online scheduling.
Learn More
